NOTE: This is reference architecture for educational and research purposes.
The mortgage underwriting decisions produced by this system are NOT real
lending decisions and are NOT certified for any regulatory use. Any
production deployment of similar architectures in regulated lending requires
independent model validation (OCC SR 11-7), Fair Lending review (ECOA / FHA),
HMDA reporting integration, operational risk assessment, and third-party
model risk management for the underlying LLM. All borrower data, bank
names, and decisions in this repository are fictional.
